second.  The third and forth missiles detonate near by burning his wings.

    Terrataur glances at Aquataur and smiles.  "Hey do you have any idea what 
a smeel is?"  She quickly responds with a negative and fires eight more optic 
blasts at Apewing.  Terrataur, likewise fires two powerful shots.
